<HTMLQuestion
    xmlns="http://mechanicalturk.amazonaws.com/AWSMechanicalTurkDataSchemas/2011-11-11/HTMLQuestion.xsd">
    <HTMLContent><![CDATA[
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv='Content-Type' content='text/html; charset=UTF-8'/>
    <script type='text/javascript' src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/mturk-public/externalHIT_v1.js'></script>
</head>
<style>
    /* Add styling for the instructions container */
    .instructions {
        border: 1px solid #ccc; /* Border style */
        padding: 10px; /* Padding to give space */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space between instructions and other content */
    }
    
    /* Additional styles for better visual appearance */
    .panel-heading {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        padding: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* New styles to create a side-by-side layout */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .image-container {
            flex: 1;
            margin-right: 10px; /* Adjust the margin as needed */
        }

        .response-options {
            flex: 1;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        /* To ensure responsive behavior */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .image-container,
            .response-options {
                margin: 0; /* Reset margins */
                flex: auto;
            }
        }
</style>
<body>
    <form name='mturk_form' method='post' id='mturk_form' action='https://www.mturk.com/mturk/externalSubmit'>
        <input type='hidden' value='' name='assignmentId' id='assignmentId'/>
        <div class="instructions">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <strong>Instructions</strong>
            </div>
        <p>
            <b>Please read all instructions carefully and then complete the question.</b> 
            By performing this HIT, you agree that<font color="red"> you have
            read the description of the study being undertaken, and give consent for the data you enter to be
            used for research.
            </font>
            &nbsp;Please 
            <a target="blank" href="https://iral.cs.umbc.edu/Consent_Form--MarguliesOgbaduClassProject.pdf">read the consent form</a>. If you would prefer not to take part in this experiment, please return this
            HIT.
        </p>
        <p>
            You will be provided an instruction issued by a human and directed at a robot to perform. 
            Your goal is to select the most appropriate response or action that the <b>robot</b> should take.
            So imagine <b><span style="color:red;">YOU are the ROBOT</span></b>. 
            You may be provided a still image of the robot's video feed from the moment the 
            human issued the instruction.
            If none of the options fit the instruction, select "None of the above".

            <p><strong>Please do the following:</strong></p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong> Read the "Human Instruction".</strong></li>
                <li><strong> Inspect the image showing the robot's video feed (if provided).</strong></li>
                <li><strong> Select the best response the robot should take from the options provided.</strong></li>
                <li><strong> Select "None of the above" if none of the options fit.</strong></li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Please do not:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong> Make a selection without reading the "Human Instruction".</strong></li>
                <li><strong> Make a selection without inspecting the image (if provided).</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class = "container">
        <div class="image-container">
            <h3> Human instruction: <span style="font-weight: normal;">""Text to Replace""</span></h3>
            <div>
                <img src='YOUR_IMAGE_URL_HERE' alt='Image Placeholder' width='600' height='400'>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="response-options">
            <h3>
                Robot response options:
            </h3>
            <div>
                <input type='radio' name='reported_signal' value='Turn'>Turn<br>
                <input type='radio' name='reported_signal' value='Move'>Move<br>
                <input type='radio' name='reported_signal' value='Send photo'>Send photo<br>
                <input type='radio' name='reported_signal' value='Stop'>Stop<br>
                <input type='radio' name='reported_signal' value='Explore'>Explore<br>
                <input type='radio' name='reported_signal' value='None of the Above'>None of the Above<br>
            </div>
            <p><input type='submit' id='submitButton' value='Submit' />
            </p>
    </div>
    </div>
</form>
<script language='Javascript'>turkSetAssignmentID();</script>
</body></html>
